THE STRATEGY OF GAME

1. In this game there is no specific guess limits, that is a player can guess at his levels & can move further in the game.
2. But the main thing is the timer!
3. If you want to increase your score, you need to guess the color right & type it rightly into the textbox provided there on screen.
4. If you guess correctly then score & timer will be incremented.
5. If guess wrong then timer will be flying as it is, thus one must be aware of time & play according to that.
